<!--<h4>First Panel.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>© svasti śrīmatu yādavanārāyaṇa pratāpacakrava
<lb n="2" break="no"/>rtti siṁghaṇadēva prithvīrājyaṁgeyyuttirdda sakavarśa
<lb n="3"/>1157 manumathasa[*]vachada phālguṇa bahuḷa 10 ma <g type="danda">.</g> ha<unclear>lu</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vāgila paṁḍyadēva Ajjaḍiyiniṟidalli baḍagi la
<lb n="5" break="no"/>khkhōja kādida pa<unclear>ri</unclear> <g type="ddanda">.</g> parideyi tāgi bharadiṁ yari
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Panel.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="6" break="no"/>gaḷa mūdalisi hoyi<unclear>saḷa</unclear>lā <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ḷoḷu haīdalu <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>paribhavisi hōda <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> palaranu <g type="ddanda">.</g> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> Ēriya
<lb n="8"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> yara māda <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ḍeyo
<lb n="9"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> suragaṇikeyaruyyalu kaḍugalitanavoppittu lakhkha
<lb n="10"/>svargaprāptaṁ <g type="ddanda">.</g>
</p>

